flowRoot.flowPara: I haven't thought of what I want to write for this section yet, but for the sake of

this project, I'm going to write nonsense. I have a German Shepherd that looks absolutely terrifying, however if you know him, he is a huge coward. We're talking an-8 inch-shaking-tail-tucked-Chihuahua probably has more courage than my dog.

He weighs over 100 pounds, he is close to being 3ft tall. His paws are just as big as my hands, his head probably weighs more than 8lbs. I love my dog very much. Someone tried to kidnap him once, but we caught them in the act. I think this is enough for now.
Something, something fresh ingredients. Something something gourmet gourmet. Michael Buble.
